OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDrier
OL,6,Fand brighter on Friday and Saturday
OL,7,Fwith perhaps the odd shower, winds
OL,8,Fmostly light too. Rain arriving from
OL,9,Fthe west on Sunday. Temperatures
OL,10,Fslowly increasing, but still below
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
